General Assembly Of North Carolina Session 2025
1 SECTION 19.(a) If any provision of this act or the application thereof to any person
2 or circumstances is held invalid, such invalidity shall not affect other provisions or applications
3 of this act that can be given effect without the invalid provision or application and, to this end,
4 the provisions of this act are declared to be severable.
5 SECTION 19.(b) Except as otherwise provided, this act is effective when it becomes
6 law.
